updates.HtmlString: Fixed: Draft booster now contains only 3 U instead of sometimes 4. Thanks, Mike!
Fixed: Prerelease seeded boosters: 2 land slots can now have family-coloured dual lands instead of just triomes.
Fixed: Prerelease seeded booster: Foil R/M now in the pack and could be any card, not just your chosen family. Riveteers seeded now has 8 C instead of 9.
Fixed: Collector booster: slot 2 now CU instead of RM, land slot now only extended art basic land. Thanks kismaa!
